content: /imagine Create a stunning, high-quality photo that captures the terrifying moment when Godzilla devours the entire planet. In the image, the lighting should be dramatic and intense, with the glow of the planet's atmosphere casting an ethereal light on the monster's terrifying features. Make the viewer feel like they are right there in the moment, watching helplessly as the giant lizard engulfs the planet in its jaws. The realism and detail of the image should be so striking that the viewer can almost hear the crunching of the earth beneath Godzilla's teeth. With your talent and expertise, create a work of art that will leave a lasting impression on those who see it.
